 memory foam layer leverages airflow to pull heat out of the top layer leaving you cool and comfortablewhy does heat flow matterwhile you’re asleep your body acts like a little thermal engine putting out the equivalent heat of a w light bulb by using foams that leverage convection heat transfer through air and conduction heat transfer through solids we’re able to pull heat away from your body and disperse it back into the atmosphereless stores more snoreswe flipped the mattress industry on its head by eliminating showrooms employing smart logistics and using compression technology to ship the casper mattress in a compact box this allows us to offer a premium mattress for a fraction of the pricered door with casper mattress boxred door with casper mattress box“changing the way people shop for mattresses” night trial free return pickupsleep on it lounge on it dream on it — if you dont love it well give you a full refund no springs attachedorder onlinefree shipping nights free return pickupexplore the trialbuild your bedthe waterproof mattress protectorguards against dirt spills and normal wear and tearshopthe foundationprovides excellent support and can be assembled in minutesshopthe metal bed frameworks with our foundation to create a complete sleep setupshopfrequently asked questionswhat setup do you recommend for the casper mattresswe designed the casper mattress to be versatile so it can work with all standard foundations as with all foam beds you want as much direct support under the mattress as possible a wooden slatted or platform bed offers the most support for optimal support under all size sizes  twin twin xl full queen king cal king   we suggest using the casper foundationwhy is the casper mattress better than its lookalikesthe engineering behind the casper mattress goes far beyond aesthetics our mattress is the result of intensive research and continuous development by our person san francisco rd team who collectively hold more than  patents unlike putting